pipeline_summary.name: extract_claims_pipeline
pipeline_summary.description: Healthcare claims processing ETL pipeline implementing a staged ETL pattern with parallel extraction, transformation, and parallel loading stages.

components.name: Extract Claims CSV
components.description: Reads claims.csv from the local filesystem and pushes the extracted claim records via XCom for downstream processing.

upstream_policy.description: Root extraction task, no upstream dependencies.

connections.purpose: Read source CSV files from local disk

components.name: Extract Providers CSV
components.description: Reads providers.csv from the local filesystem and pushes the extracted provider records via XCom for downstream processing.

upstream_policy.description: Root extraction task, no upstream dependencies.

connections.purpose: Read source CSV files from local disk

components.name: Join Claims and Providers, Anonymize PII, Calculate Risk Scores
components.description: Joins extracted claim and provider records, anonymizes personally identifiable information, and computes risk scores for each claim.

upstream_policy.description: Executes after both extract_claims and extract_providers complete successfully.

components.name: Load Transformed Data to Data Warehouse
components.description: Writes the transformed claimprovider dataset into the healthcare_analytics PostgreSQL warehouse tables claims_fact and providers_dim.

connections.purpose: Write transformed data to PostgreSQL analytics warehouse

components.name: Refresh BI Dashboards
components.description: Triggers refresh operations for Power BI and Tableau dashboards after the warehouse load completes.

connections.purpose: Invoke Power BI and Tableau refresh endpoints
